PUBLIC  公開

Harish Kakani
#: 361 296 5393
@: Harishkakani@Gmail.com

Professional Summary

 11  years  of  professional  software  experience  in  IT  Industry  including
Design, Development, Maintenance, Enhancement, load and performance
testing  and  Production  Support  of  Web  and  Mobile  based  Business
Applications. 

 Expertise  in  Microsoft  technologies(Cloud,  Bots,  Web,  Mobile,
Reporting, Repository & Load Testing) like Bots Framework, Azure
Cloud, Azure AD & SSO, Azure Service Bus, Xamarin, Microsoft
Power  BI,  Microsoft  Power  Apps,  Angular,  Type  Script,
Swagger,  .Net  core,  Web  API,  GIT,  SendGrid,  ASP.NET  MVC,
ASP.NET Web Forms, C#, LINQ, ENTITY FRAME WORK, XML Web
Services,  WCF  SERVICES,  AJAX,  IIS,  SQL  Server,  Boot  Strap,
SSRS, TFS, Load testing and Performance testing.

 Good Exposure on Automobile, Financial, E-Commerce, Travel, Risk
analysis and staffing domains.

 Good  experience  in  developing  Chat  Bots and  deployed  on  multiple
channels. 

 Excellent  experience  in  develop  Azure Cloud  Solutions across
enterprise.  

 Good experience in developing Micro Service-based Architecture. 
 Experience Data exchange service like Service Bus & Event Grid.
 Experience in integrating SSO using cloud AD.
 Developing  SPA application  in  using  Angular,  Type  script  and  Micro

service using .Net Core.
 Mobile solutions development using Xamarin Forms.
 Report Development using Microsoft Power BI.
 Develop quick small applications using Microsoft Power apps.  
 Deploy applications using Azure DevOps and Quick Build.
 Experience  in  developing  applications  of  N-tier  Architecture with

Presentation, BLL (Business Logic Layer), and DAL (Data Access Layer)
components.

 Good  experience  with  Visual  Studio  Enterprise  and  Professional
versions (2017, 2015, 2013, 2010, 2008, 2005 and 2003) and VS
Code as IDE in developing Cloud, Bots, Web and Mobile applications. 

 Good experience in writing  Stored Procedures, Sub Queries, Views
and Joins using SQL Server 2017/2015/2012/2008/2005.

 Experience in working with version control  tools like  GIT, Bit Bucket,
TFS (Team Foundation Server) and Microsoft VSS (Visual Source Safe).

 Worked extensively on  Swagger,  Postman and  SoapUI Open Source
Functional testing tool for WebAPI and Web service testing.

 Excellent  understanding  of  software  development  life  cycle  including
Agile methodology (Scrum) and Waterfall methodology.

http://www.soapui.org/


PUBLIC  公開

Harish Kakani
#: 361 296 5393
@: Harishkakani@Gmail.com

 Experience  in  Performance  testing,  Load  testing and  scheduling
them using Visual Studio enterprise version.

 Experience in  optimization of  stored  procedures  and code  to  improve
performance based on the load test results.

 Participate in Code review and Design review.
 Experience in preparing POC for common tasks including documentation

for integration.
 Experience in preparing problem analysis documents.
 Employing  best  practices  and  proven  development  procedures  which

serve to optimize the development cycle and improve code quality.
 Support  and  handle  any  problems  during  and  post  deployment  using

ServiceNow and BMC Remedy.
 Supported  and  handled  deployment  across  all  environments  and

maintained source code for each environment in Git, Bitbucket & TFS.
 Experience giving walk through to users and testing whenever required.

 Very Good experience in handling clients & meeting their requirements
and willing to adopt new technologies/work environments, well organized
Analytical & Leadership skills.

Professional Experience

 Working as Sr. Software with Computech Corporation, Detroit.
 Worked with CES USA Ltd, Detroit.
 Worked with Serve all Enterprise solutions Ltd (Division of 

Computech Corporation), Hyderabad.

Education 

 Bachelor in Electronic and Communications, JNTU, Hyderabad, India.

Events and Trainings 

 Microsoft Build 2018. ( https://channel9.msdn.com/Events/Build/2018 )

Technical Skills

 Azure Cloud:   Azure AD & SSO, Azure Service Bus, SendGrid, Power 
Apps, Azure DevOps.

 . Net Technologies :  Bots Framework, Xamarin, .Net coré, EF Coré, 
ASP.NET (MVC and Web Forms), ADO.NET, LINQ, Entity Framework, T4 
Templates, POCO Objects, Swagger. 

 Languages: C#, SQL, PL-SQL

https://channel9.msdn.com/Events/Build/2018


PUBLIC  公開

Harish Kakani
#: 361 296 5393
@: Harishkakani@Gmail.com

 Web Technologies:  Web API, Power Shell, Type Script, Boot Strap, 
HTML 5, CSS, JavaScript, TypeScript, jQuery, XML, Restful Services, 
WCF, Web Services, SOAP, WSDL, AJAX tool kit.

 GUI and IDE:  VS Code and Visual Studio.NET 
2003/2005/2008/2010/2013/2015/2017.

 RDBMS / DBMS:  SQL Server 2017/2014/2012/2008 /2005. Oracle. 
 Version Controller:  Bitbucket, Git, Team foundation server (TFS), 

Visual SourceSafe (VSS), SVN.
 Reporting: SSRS and Power BI
